---
---
<section class="people" aria-labelledby="people-heading">
  <figure class="photo">
    <img
      src="/people-family.jpg"
      alt="A multi-generational family gathered on the front steps of their home, talking together."
      loading="lazy"
      width="1200"
      height="800"
    />
    <figcaption class="photo-cap">Photo: Pexels</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class="copy">
    <p class="section-eyebrow eyebrow-blue">Who Bennies is for</p>
    <h2 id="people-heading" class="section-title">
      For anyone who's ever wondered, <span class="hl hl-blue">"am I eligible?"</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="lede">
      The parent trying to feed their kids. The veteran waiting on a disability decision.
      The senior on a fixed income. The neighbor who lost work last month.
      The immigrant who doesn't know where to start.
    </p>
    <p class="lede">
      If you've ever felt overwhelmed by paperwork, unsure what you qualify for,
      or afraid to ask — Bennies is for you.
    </p>

    <ul class="tags" aria-label="Who we serve">
      <li>Families with children</li>
      <li>Seniors on fixed incomes</li>
      <li>Veterans</li>
      <li>People with disabilities</li>
      <li>Students &amp; recent grads</li>
      <li>Anyone between jobs</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .people {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 72px 0;
  }
  .photo {
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;
  }
  .photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .photo-cap {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 10px;
    right: 12px;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.55);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .copy .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .lede {
    color: var(--ink-2);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    max-width: 34rem;
  }
  .tags {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .tags li {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--surface-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue-strong);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .people { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; padding: 48px 0; }
  }
</style>
